title: Shields Up
author: Friendly Neighbor
Takarada
Derpy Horse
description: Originally formed by the Steam user Direstorm, Shields Up is the combination of five different mods: Shields Up, Friendly Technology, Alphean's Random Expansion, Pompano's Ever Expanding Galaxy, Tufton's Plugin, That Someone's Plugin, and a number of ships from Mdsmestad. Shields Up provides a plethora of new experiences with multiple new alien races, all with their own ships and technologies, as well as even more ships and outfits for the human race, Shields Up is the largest Endless Sky mod to date!
